<section id="i-cant-breathe." class="level1">
<h1>I can’t breathe.</h1>
<p>This wasn’t supposed to happen.<br>
I’m not stupid.<br>
I’m not stupid.<br>
Am I?<br>
There are no options remaining. There is no hope of recovery. I must flee the country.</p>
<p>Yesterday, something terrifying happened. Something I still don’t fully understand. Am I reaching the edge of my ability?</p>
<section id="i-havent-failed-before." class="level3">
<h3 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="i-havent-failed-before.">I haven’t <strong>failed</strong> before.</h3>
<p>What do I do now?</p>
